main event: Kenneth Arnold, a private pilot, reported sighting 9 disc-like craft flying over Mount Rainier, Washington on June 24, 1947 at around 3:00 PM.
interesting points: The objects were traveling at an estimated speed of 1,200 miles per hour.
The objects were observed flying in a chain with an erratic motion and slight side-to-side dipping.
The observer, Kenneth Arnold, was flying his own private plane at an altitude of approximately 9,500 feet.
The weather conditions were clear with bright sunlight.
No photographs were taken, and there were no other witnesses.
